{
  "info": {
    "name": "PR Manager Admin API - Personal Secrets",
    "description": "Admin API collection with per-user admin secrets. Create your secret with: npm run admin:create-secret",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "üìñ SETUP INSTRUCTIONS",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1Ô∏è‚É£ Create Your Admin Secret",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "https://example.com"
          },
          "response": [],
          "description": "RUN IN TERMINAL:\n\n```bash\nnpm run admin:create-secret\n```\n\nThen:\n1. Enter your email\n2. Enter a name (e.g., \"Postman\")\n3. Copy the generated secret\n\n‚úÖ That's it! Now paste the secret in the {{ADMIN_SECRET}} variable below"
        },
        {
          "name": "2Ô∏è‚É£ Set Postman Variables",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "https://example.com"
          },
          "response": [],
          "description": "1. Click on the Environment icon (top right)\n2. Click \"Edit\" on your environment\n3. Set these variables:\n   - API_URL: http://localhost:3001\n   - ADMIN_SECRET: (paste your generated secret here)\n\n‚úÖ Done! All requests will use your secret automatically"
        },
        {
          "name": "3Ô∏è‚É£ Test Connection",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "AdminSecret {{ADMIN_SECRET}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{API_URL}}/admin/health",
              "host": ["{{API_URL}}"],
              "path": ["admin", "health"]
            },
            "description": "Click Send - if you see system health metrics, you're all set! ‚úÖ"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "System",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "AdminSecret {{ADMIN_SECRET}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{API_URL}}/admin/health",
              "host": ["{{API_URL}}"],
